{"tid":567643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"unwire：高院頒令 樂視清盤","createTime":"2018-02-21T05:07:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T08:51:39.000Z","uid":40672,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f41065c68919a7c506ac51e498e63a18b65a2110","tid":567643,"uid":40672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T05:07:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/02/21/letv-liquidation/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F02%2F21%2Fletv-liquidation%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=aRUSysLZ%2BeaNkx2Uih%2FT4pWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=56e26490\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/02/21/letv-liquidation/fun-tech/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f95ff92e96314ea2138c9e7f718a6fe372a4352","tid":567643,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T05:08:33.000Z","msg":"高院正式頒令：樂視清盤<br />\n讚好此文:<br />\n二月 21, 2018 &bull;科技趣聞 &bull;<br />\n<br />\n樂視香港近年飽受財務狀況困擾，旗下的樂視有限公司（LE CorporationLimited）更於去年 12 月 1 日入稟高等法院申請自行清盤。案件排期至今（21日）於高等法院提訊，並獲聆案官正式頒下清盤令。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據資料顯示，樂視香港旗下有多間公司，包括擁有香港英超播映權的樂視體育，以及進行清盤的樂視有限公司。自去年起，樂視有限公司已被多間公司入稟追債，當中包括被室內設計公司於去年 8 月入稟，追討 121 萬元工程費用。<br />\n<br />\n至於樂視體育亦曾被多次入稟，去年先後被追討 850 萬元牌照費及 189 萬元。去年 8 月，更被溫布頓網球賽的主辦單位 The All English Lawn Tennis Club（Championships）Ltd 入稟申請清盤，但其後被撤回。<br />\n<br />\n前樂視亞太區總裁莫翠天早前回應媒體查詢時表示，樂視有限公司的業務以管理樂視盒子及電視為主，與樂視體育是兩間完全獨立的公司。"},{"pid":"0b059eb330cd73df98d9bc7d4cc352769a54d94b","tid":567643,"uid":40672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f95ff92e96314ea2138c9e7f718a6fe372a4352","tid":567643,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T05:08:33.000Z","msg":"高院正式頒令：樂視清盤<br />\n讚好此文:<br />\n二月 21, 2018 &bull;科技趣聞 &bull;<br />\n<br />\n樂視香港近年飽受財務狀況困擾，旗下的樂視有限公司（LE CorporationLimited）更於去年 12 月 1 日入稟高等法院申請自行清盤。案件排期至今（21日）於高等法院提訊，並獲聆案官正式頒下清盤令。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據資料顯示，樂視香港旗下有多間公司，包括擁有香港英超播映權的樂視體育，以及進行清盤的樂視有限公司。自去年起，樂視有限公司已被多間公司入稟追債，當中包括被室內設計公司於去年 8 月入稟，追討 121 萬元工程費用。<br />\n<br />\n至於樂視體育亦曾被多次入稟，去年先後被追討 850 萬元牌照費及 189 萬元。去年 8 月，更被溫布頓網球賽的主辦單位 The All English Lawn Tennis Club（Championships）Ltd 入稟申請清盤，但其後被撤回。<br />\n<br />\n前樂視亞太區總裁莫翠天早前回應媒體查詢時表示，樂視有限公司的業務以管理樂視盒子及電視為主，與樂視體育是兩間完全獨立的公司。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T05:08:57.000Z","msg":"唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be7892abd712c07e7470a4745df878a698f9bde7","tid":567643,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T05:09:12.000Z","msg":"唔係有英超個樂視體育黎架<br />\n<br />\n但都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd73c7904ab6546c31f313fa98c89c205368b6f6","tid":567643,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T05:21:51.000Z","msg":"下一間 海航"},{"pid":"7997af7847b03de2803fab56dd83cb5164cf4bc6","tid":567643,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be7892abd712c07e7470a4745df878a698f9bde7","tid":567643,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T05:09:12.000Z","msg":"唔係有英超個樂視體育黎架<br />\n<br />\n但都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img sr